<add><ab facs="#facs_225_r1l19">vns die </ab></add> die das getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_225_r1l22">nicht cʒüverſprechen ſteen / vnd wir der cʒemal nicht mechtig ſein / vnd daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_225_r1l23">vvir vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> keinerley ſchulde dar an <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>re</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_225_r1l24"><expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ıſt / . So <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ Valcʒner 
